text: Atifete Jahjaga (born 20 April 1975) is the fourth President of Kosovo.Koha, "Në krye të Policisë së Kosovës, Atifete Jahjaga" Shqip TIME.mk 16 October 2010 (accessed 6 April 2011) She was the first female President of the Republic of Kosovo."Kush do të na udhëheq" Telegrafi.com 7 April 2011 (accessed 7 April 2011) ==References== ==Other websites== *Facebook *Twitter Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Kosovo
